This directory should contain the following:
- applcation properties file
- keyfiles
- certificate files
- static configuration files
- executatble files (shell/python/java)


NOTE:
   While putting keyfile in the directory kindly encrypt them by using the ansible-vault utility. Command to encrypt a file using ansible-vault is as follows:
        $ ansible-vault encrypt <file-name>

   Provide the encryption password when you are prompted.

   To use the encrypted file in playbooks, execute the ansible-playbook command in the following way:
       
       $ ansible-playbook <playbook-name> --ask-vault-pass
 
